gomodel:SYNGO_1321  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: identification of 374 proteins in purified PSD fractions from rat forebrain. In addition to uncovering many previously unknown putative components of the PSD, the LC-MS/MS analysis was also exploited to provide relative abundancy information, and to identify 13 specific phosphorylation sites in eight PSD proteins.. Experimental description: Adult rat brain" ;
